txt.en: 'I'll take care of these Dwarves. You go on and find Skogrim!'
'They haven't thought to guard the hidden door. That will be their undoing!'
'Giants! This may be a harder fight than I thought....'
'So Skorgrim is finally dead? Ha,ha! Good work!'
'Time has been cruel to this mechanism...'
'Ha, ha! Victory is ours! My tally is.. umm... Blast! I lost count!'
'Now to find the Nazgûl and Skorgrím!'
'I will use the keystone to open the door!'
'All right. Let's go. Be careful, there must be foes about.'
'Let us rest here a moment, and then we will see about ending these villains!'
